title: Valar Rereadis: The Sworn Sword - Part 2
description:
We discuss the Old Lion, the Little Lion, the decline of House Osgrey through obsolescence, the boot and the blood price, comparisons to Lord of the Rings and Dune, lots of humorous moments, the "true steel" and Wat and Wat and Wat.
